          </div>
          <div class="options">
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="a">Small chest/buttocks and low body fat<br><br>
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="b">Broad Squared Shoulders<br><br>
            <input type="radio" name="q7" value="c">Body fat mainly in lower abdomen<br>
          </div>
        </div>
<div id="question8">
          <div class="question">
            Q8. Choose the most appropriate?
          </div>
          <div class="options">
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="a">Linear physique with low body fat<br><br>
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="b">Naturally strong and muscular<br><br>
            <input type="radio" name="q8" value="c">High levels of body fat<br>
          </div>
        </div>
<div id="question9">
          <div class="question">
            Q9. Choose your body shape?
